  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study was to illustrate surgeons' own perception of fatigue and the impact
      they felt it had on their performance. This was accomplished through a focus group study,
      where 13 surgeons participated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
